TopicTitle: update in launcher fail code 23 error

Articles.Content:
It's unmoded, 64-bit, win7 NON Steam version.

I can't update it to .25 It says:

rsync error: some files/attrs were not transferred (see previous errors) (code 23) at /home/lapo/package/rsync-3.0.9-1/src/rsync-3.0.9/main.c(1518) [generator=3.0.9]

rsync exited with code 23: Partial transfer due to error

Any ideas?

BTW, previous version is playing fine.

Edited October 10, 2014 by Ski
IIRC, Patcher doesn't support Windows 64-bit KSP, so you'll have to update manually.

What I'd try:

Rename your existing KSP game folder to ksp_old, so you still have what you have. Then create an empty directory with the original directory name, giving the patcher an empty playing field to work with.

I'm going to go out on a limb and guess that rsync is encountering a file where the source and destination files both claim to be 'newer'. That's been the usual problem I encounter when using rsync.

May not work, but it's a five-second fix if it does.
